  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Adjournment of case against Sambika",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The case against Member of Parliament Patali Sampika Ranawaka for driving dangerously and injuring one person in Welikada police station has been adjourned till August 31.",
        "The case will be taken up for hearing on August 31 to give an opportunity to put forward the basic objection that the defendant side, Sampika Ranavaka intends to put forward that the said case cannot be taken forward.",
        "The case came up for hearing on Monday (18) before Colombo High Court Judge Namal Palalle. Deputy Solicitor General Madhava Thennakone appeared in the court on behalf of the Attorney General. President's Counsel Sarath Jayamanna appeared in the forum on behalf of Sampika Ranavaka.",
        "Accordingly, the president's lawyer Sarath Jayamanna, who presented the issues in the forum, put forward a basic objection that the case could not be taken forward.",
        "At this stage, the case was adjourned till August 31 for presentation of arguments on the basic objections."
      ],
